lambda function:-

 lambda function is a one-line function
lambda syntax:-
function_name = lambda parameters: expression

exception handling:-

there are different types of exception handling:
zero division error, value error, etc


global variable and local variable

declare a global variable with a keyword inside the function to use outside the function.




